SELECT * FROM Patients;

SELECT provider_id, first_name, specialty FROM Providers;
SELECT * FROM TelepsychiatryAppointments WHERE appointment_date >= NOW();
SELECT patient_id, record_date, diagnosis FROM HealthRecords ORDER BY record_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Patients ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT patient_id, first_name, last_name, gender FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Female';

SELECT Patients.first_name, Patients.last_name, TelepsychiatryAppointments.appointment_date FROM Patients JOIN TelepsychiatryAppointments ON Patients.patient_id = TelepsychiatryAppointments.patient_id ORDER BY TelepsychiatryAppointments.appointment_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT Patients.first_name, Patients.last_name, Providers.first_name AS provider_first_name, Providers.last_name AS provider_last_name FROM Patients JOIN TelepsychiatryAppointments ON Patients.patient_id = TelepsychiatryAppointments.patient_id JOIN Providers ON TelepsychiatryAppointments.provider_id = Providers.provider_id ORDER BY Patients.last_name ASC, TelepsychiatryAppointments.appointment_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT Patients.first_name, COUNT(HealthRecords.record_id) AS num_records FROM Patients LEFT JOIN HealthRecords ON Patients.patient_id = HealthRecords.patient_id GROUP BY Patients.first_name HAVING num_records > 0 ORDER BY num_records DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT hospital_name, location FROM hospital ORDER BY hospital_name DESC;
SELECT psychiatrist_name, specialty FROM psychiatrist WHERE hospital_id = 1;
SELECT symptoms, diagnosis FROM electronic_health_record WHERE ehr_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_patient WHERE psychiatrist_id IN (SELECT psychiatrist_id FROM psychiatrist WHERE specialty='Anxiety Disorders')

SELECT telepsychiatry_patient.patient_name, electronic_health_record.diagnosis, hospital.hospital_name FROM telepsychiatry_patient JOIN electronic_health_record ON telepsychiatry_patient.patient_id = electronic_health_record.patient_id JOIN hospital ON psychiatrist.hospital_id = hospital.hospital_id WHERE electronic_health_record.date_of_visit > '2022-01-01'

SELECT telepsychiatry_patient.patient_name, psychiatrist.psychiatrist_name, psychiatrist.specialty FROM telepsychiatry_patient JOIN psychiatrist ON telepsychiatry_patient.psychiatrist_id = psychiatrist.psychiatrist_id WHERE psychiatrist.specialty = 'Depression Management' ORDER BY telepsychiatry_patient.patient_name ASC

SELECT telepsychiatry_patient.patient_name, electronic_health_record.symptoms, patient_care_plan.care_plan_details FROM telepsychiatry_patient JOIN electronic_health_record ON telepsychiatry_patient.patient_id = electronic_health_record.patient_id JOIN patient_care_plan ON telepsychiatry_patient.patient_id = patient_care_plan.patient_id WHERE patient_care_plan.care_plan_details LIKE '%medication%'
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT psychiatrist_id) AS unique_psychiatrists, COUNT(patient_id) AS total_patients FROM telepsychiatry_patient
